arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	id_RunestoneGizmo = idActorGizmo
	
	ID_Clone_Druid = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(NPC_SCHOLAR_QUESTGIVER)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_Clone_Druid) then
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_Clone_Druid, ID_NPC_RUNESTONE_POSITION)
		Hydra.QActorAnimLoop(ID_Clone_Druid, S_POWER_USE, 3)
		Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_Clone_Druid, S_RUNESTONE_ACTIVATE_FAIL_FXGROUP)
		Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(ID_Clone_Druid, "AnimKey_Neutral")
		Hydra.QActorWait(ID_Clone_Druid, 2)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_Clone_Druid, NPC_SCHOLAR_QUESTGIVER)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_Clone_Druid)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_YUEIN_PT2, idQuestOwnerPlayer, ID_Clone_Druid)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_Clone_Druid, S_CONVO_YUEIN_PT2)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(ID_Clone_Druid)
	end

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	idSelf = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	idPlayer = idActorPlayer
	
	tPlayersInParty = Hydra.PlayerActorsInParty(idSelf)

	ID_Clone_Druid = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(NPC_SCHOLAR_QUESTGIVER)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_Clone_Druid) then	
		-- Clone Theater
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_Clone_Druid, ID_NPC_RUNESTONE_POSITION)
		Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_Clone_Druid, S_OUTRO_EFFECTGRP)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_Clone_Druid)
		id_ChargeFX = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, S_CHARGED_EFFECT, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorWait(ID_Clone_Druid, 3)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_OUTRO1, idPlayer, ID_Clone_Druid)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_Clone_Druid, S_CONVO_OUTRO1)
		Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(ID_Clone_Druid, "AnimKey_Neutral")
		Hydra.QActorWait(ID_Clone_Druid, 0.3)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_OUTRO2, idPlayer, ID_Clone_Druid)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_Clone_Druid, NPC_SCHOLAR_QUESTGIVER)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_Clone_Druid, S_CONVO_OUTRO2)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(ID_Clone_Druid)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_Clone_Druid)
		
		for i,actorPlayerID in ipairs(tPlayersInParty) do
		
			if Hydra.PlayerIsLocalCoOp(actorPlayerID) then
		
				-- Send Cue to Self for Local Co-Op Player who doesn't have a clone
				Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_Scos_TheDiviner_StoneTheater01", idSelf, actorPlayerID)
			
			else
		
				Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_Scos_TheDiviner_StoneTheater01", idSelf, idSelf)
			
			end
		end	
	end
end

function Start()
	-- Restart the VFX if it is already there
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_ChargeFX) then
		if Hydra.ActorComplexEffectIsValid(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, id_ChargeFX) then
		
		else
			id_ChargeFX = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, S_CHARGED_EFFECT, true)
			Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, 1.5)
		end
	else
		id_ChargeFX = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, S_CHARGED_EFFECT, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, 1.5)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_ChargeFX) then
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(ID_PRIME_RUNESTONE_FINALE, id_ChargeFX)
end

Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_OUTRO3, idActorPlayer, NPC_SCHOLAR_QUESTGIVER)
	
end

szOnAbandonScript:
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_Clone_Druid) then
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ID_Clone_Druid, 0.1)
end

--if Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(S_DETECTION_AURA, "RUNESTONE_DETECT_BUFF", idSelf) then

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(NPC_SCHOLAR_QUESTGIVER) then
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(NPC_SCHOLAR_QUESTGIVER, true)
end

--Hydra.ResetPlayerVariable(idQuestOwnerPlayer, "QST_Scos_TheDiviner_Runestone03_Active")

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_ChargeFX) then

	end
end
